text: No prob %1, I went ahead and originated a call for you to %2
Got it man, we're about to find out if the fridge is running @ %2
Calling %2, because %1 wants to know if they have Prince Albert in a can
%1, this is a test where I say %2
!%2 isn't a command I know. I'd try !help
Sorry %1, I don't know the command !%2 (try !help)
Dang, %1, no one has programmed !%2 -- my developers must be lazy. (try !help)
!crank expects a format like: !crank "<crank text>" <10 digit number>
Hey %1, is !%2 a spelling mistake? My developers are omnicient and coded everything a bot could do, except misspellings (try !help)
Dang it! I tried to retrieve that pastebin entry, but I got error code: %1
Damn, I didn't see the pastebin.com ID on your URL, check the URL you pasted.
!pastecrank expects a format like: !pastecrank http://pastebin.com/identifier <10 digit number>
Yo %1, ummm... Someone's already making a crank call, and we're just using a lowly single voice channel for this, sorry man (try later)
Hey %1, there's already a call in progress (try again in a few.)
Big gulps huh? Welp, see ya later. (There's already a call in progress, %1)
Duuuude, someone is already making a crank. You'll have to try again, %1
Hey %1, %2 sent you a note %3, saying: %4
%1, !note expects a nick, and a message like: !note somedude hey you'll hear this next time you talk
Cool %1, I'll let them know next time they're active.
Dually noted.
Got that save for you %1; letting 'em know asap.
Hey %1, was that a joke about their mom? I can't save that (just kidding, saved the note for you)
Saved that note by printing it on a dot-matrix printer @ 300 dB. Or, just saved it to a db and I'll regurgitate it later.
You can find help @ https://code.google.com/p/whistler-bot/wiki/Help
